    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six maintains factory compression across all cylinders, with the VANOS system recently overhauled and rod bearings replaced as preventative measures. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is flawless, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a suspension setup that retains its factory-spec damping and bushing elasticity. Finished in Carbon Black with exceptional paint depth and zero oxidation, this unit represents a collector-grade preservation of BMW\u2019s peak analog engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
