    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, glass-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery retains its original matte finish and factory-fresh scent, with no bolster wear or creasing. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records, documenting a 'no-expense-spared' maintenance philosophy. The engine bay is pristine, free of any leaks or dust, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. If you are looking for the finest specimen on the market\u2014one that requires absolutely nothing but a new appreciative owner\u2014this is the vehicle for you.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
